### [Nehemiah Chapter 13](../../../bib/kjv/neh013.htm#001.md)

[Nehemiah](../../../bib/kjv/neh001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">neh 13:0</span></span>

Overview

[Neh 13:1](../../../bib/kjv/neh013.htm#001.md), Upon the reading of the
law, separation is made from the mixed multitude; [Neh
13:4](../../../bib/kjv/neh013.htm#004.md), Nehemiah, at his return, causes
the chambers to be cleansed; [Neh
13:10](../../../bib/kjv/neh013.htm#010.md), He reforms the offices in the
house of God; [Neh 13:15](../../../bib/kjv/neh013.htm#015.md), the
violation of the sabbath; [Neh 13:23](../../../bib/kjv/neh013.htm#023.md),
and the marriages with the strange wives.

